snippet.title: Eat Carbs Outdoors
snippet.description:
Just sharing some of my dirt time, gear, and outings. I'm not a professional outdoorsman or anything. I just like what I do.
The outdoors is a hobby for me.. and I love it. My aim is to keep it real and post it as it happens. 

Check out my Facebook page.
https://www.facebook.com/pages/Eat-Carbs/626922257383004?sk=timeline
